      <title>法国政党的购买力计划耗资超过 100 亿欧元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/french-party-spending-power-plans-cost-over-10-billion-a-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[参加法国立法议会选举的三大政治党派已作出竞选承诺，仅在支出能力部分，每个党派每年将花费超过 100 亿欧元（107 亿美元），尽管法国已在苦苦挣扎削减预算赤字。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/french-party-spending-power-plans-cost-over-10-billion-a-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 04:45:10 GMT</pubDate>
